name: pyntacle
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyntacle" %}
{% set version = "1.3.2" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/pyntacle-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 95f6aecc52794cc7a7eeb89773791c498b394874c01ade8a4ce85a0384e07513

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - pyntacle = pyntacle.pyntacle:App
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - numpy
    - pip
    - python >=3.6,<3.8
  run:
    - colorama ==0.4.4
    - numba ==0.51.2
    - ordered-set ==4.0.2
    - pandas ==1.1.4
    - psutil
    - python >=3.6,<3.8
    - python-igraph ==0.8.3
    - seaborn ==0.11.0
    - setuptools
    - xlsxwriter ==1.3.7

test:
  imports:
    - pyntacle
    - pyntacle.algorithms
  commands:
    - pip check
    - pyntacle --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://pyntacle.css-mendel.it
  summary: A Python package for network analysis based on non-canonical metrics and HPC-Computing
  dev_url: https://github.com/mazzalab/pyntacle
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - admax18
